  "title": "QC Technician #82057",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturer – Dairy Products</li><li>Position Title: <strong>QC Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Pioneer</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon to Fri: 8:00am – 8.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $2500 Basic + OT + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Check the production line before start-up and after changeover.</li><li>Do hygiene and GMP checks.</li><li>Check OPRP/CCP readings every 2 hours.</li><li>Take product and raw material samples for lab testing.</li><li>Collect flash-out powder samples during product change.</li><li>Monitor whey/flash-out powder stock and request top-up when low.</li><li>Do swab tests on machines, work area, and workers’ hands.</li><li>Fill in quality and production records correctly.</li><li>Record any issues and the actions taken.</li><li>Download data logger records weekly.</li><li>Isolate non-conforming raw materials or finished goods.</li><li>Report quality issues to QC/QA and support investigation.</li><li>Follow GMP, HACCP, and company SOPs.</li><li>Support pest control and foreign object control when needed.</li><li>Do other QC tasks assigned by your supervisor.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Basic knowledge of GMP, HACCP, and food safety.</li><li>Experience in food factory/QC is a plus.</li><li>Comfortable working in a production environment.</li><li>Able to work 12-hour rotating day and night shifts.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82057 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
